    <h1>Seismometers</h1> 
    <div style="background: #f1f1f1; float: right; margin-left: 10px; width: 300px; border: 2px solid; padding: 10px;"> 
     <h3 style="margin-top: 0px"> On this Page</h3> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
     <a href="#1">What is a seismometer?</a>
     <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
     <a href="#2">What types of educational</a>
     <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
     <a href="#2">seismometers are available?</a>
     <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
     <a href="#3">How do I obtain a seismometer?</a>
     <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
     <a href="#4">AS-1 Assembly and Installation guide</a>
     <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
     <a href="#5">Displaying your station in realtime</a>
     <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
